Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.51,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,何処だ　ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.37,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人是……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.37,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,彼らは
